snippet.title: Fur Fighters: Viggo's Revenge Trailer
snippet.description:
This was from Demo Disc 5 of the Australian PS2 Official Magazine.

This trailer is Fur Fighters: Viggo's Revenge

Notes from Uploader:
Even though it clearly says Fur Fighters, this is for the PS2 remaster, so it's for Viggo's Revenge.
And yes, you get to hear the glory of Flea's theme! They could've used the Fur Fighters theme, but they went with this!
Don't even THINK i don't see you using an invincibility cheat, trailer, I DON'T SEE THAT 100 DROPPING!
